page.content: {Trees and plants There are many trees and plants in{ {Hurst Green}because it is in the countryside. The main things are{wild {flowers, Oak, Evergreens}and many different kinds of{shrubs}and{grasses including{Wheat,Barley}and other crops.{Hawthorn}is probably the most seen. In a wood or on a public path you may see quite a few dead trees for a number of reasons. For example Squirrels, rotting, fires. {Animals Many animals like{pigeons,foxes}and rabbits live in surrounding woodland. There are also many pond living creatures like{Sticklebacks}and Tadpoles. Fishing is a very popular sport and fish like{chubb, carp}and{pike.}Many rivers now are polluted.
